          <msContents>
            <summary>Four treatises on astrolabes and astronomy, the first and fourth treatise are incomplete; the first treatise skips from chapter 22 to chapter 30 (f. 5-6) and the fourth treatise is missing some amount of the beginning, the first complete section is "taṣtīḥ dāʼirat al-ufuq" (f. 14r).</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="ara">Arabic</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Four treatises on astrolabes and astronomy.</title>
              <author>
                <persName type="authority">Qusṭā ibn Lūqā, approximately 820-approximately 912</persName>
                <persName type="vernacular">قسطا بن لوقا،</persName>
              </author>
              <author>
                <persName type="authority">ʻAlī al-Riyāḍī al-Munajjim, active 1543</persName>
                <persName type="vernacular">علي الرياضي المنجم،</persName>
              </author>
              <respStmt>
                <resp>former owner</resp>
                <persName type="authority">Aga Khan, Sadruddin, Prince, 1933-2003</persName>
              </respStmt>
            </msItem>
